<author>Hatton, John (1710-1793), Watts, Isaac (1674-1748), Chris Tomlin, Isaac Watts, Jesse Reeves, J.D. Walt, Lowell Mason</author>
<title>Mai Cetonmu, Kan Giciyenka LW67</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Mai Cetonmu, kan giciyenka,
 Ka shaida mana ƙaunarka,
 Raɗaɗinka cetonmu ne,
 Jininka kuma ranmu ne.

[V2]
 2) Mu naka ne, Mai Fansarmu,
 Da jininka ka cece mu,
 Ka kwance mu da ikonka,
 Har ka maishe mu ƴaƴanka.

[V3]
 3) Mu naka ne, Shugabanmu,
 Jikinmu, ranmu, ruhunmu,
 An saye mu da jininka,
 Domin mu aika nufinka.

[V4]
 4) Gurasar rai, ciyad da mu,
 Rijiyar rai, shayad da mu,
 Ka ba mu ruhun yardar rai,
 Ka tsarkake mu fa sosai.</lyrics>
</song>